<p>
The site for the 1997 Conference is at the Asilomar Conference Grounds,
in Pacific Grove, CA. The grounds border the Pacific Ocean and are close
to Carmel and the scenic Seventeen Mile Drive in Pebble Beach.
<p>
The Conference is organized in cooperation with: The Naval Postgraduate
School, Monterey, CA, San Jose State University, San Jose, CA, and
the IEEE Signal Processing Society.
